{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2159, "height": 2981, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "text", "block_content": "三四一", "block_bbox": [137, 2228, 192, 2342], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "字元凯。咸宁四年（278）任镇南大将军，都督荆州诸军事，镇襄阳，以功封当阳县侯。博学而多谋略，时号“杜武库”，后人遂以“武库”为堂号。", "block_bbox": [327, 254, 1938, 374], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "7.浣花堂：以杜甫在成都浣花溪建草堂而居得名。", "block_bbox": [421, 396, 1406, 445], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "8.继善堂：海南杜氏始祖杜仲儒之孙，杜凤岐之子，三世祖杜汝善，字连元，生于宋元符年间（1098），任吉阳军千户。他淹通经史，素有名望，退休后闲赋在家，后来前往儋州作继善堂，宋朝名臣胡铨为跋记，参政李光赠诗。", "block_bbox": [327, 466, 1938, 658], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "其他堂号还有：振德堂、永言堂、清介堂、泽裕堂、敦本堂、敦义堂、瑞庆堂、余庆堂等。\n", "block_bbox": [329, 679, 1937, 802], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "三杜氏楹联", "block_bbox": [979, 892, 1282, 946], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "一、楹联", "block_bbox": [420, 1041, 619, 1089], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "重要的杜姓楹联有以下四副：", "block_bbox": [412, 1114, 986, 1163], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "1.书成通典；名列瀛洲。", "block_bbox": [425, 1189, 897, 1235], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "上联典指唐朝史学家杜佑用三十年左右时间，著《通典》二百卷。下联典指唐初良相杜如晦，助李世民开创“贞观之治”，名列凌烟阁第一事。", "block_bbox": [327, 1261, 1941, 1384], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "2.民歌慈母；世号诗王。", "block_bbox": [422, 1408, 898, 1455], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "上联典指东汉侍御史、南阳太守杜诗被称“前有召父（召信臣），后有杜母。下联典指“诗王”，是对唐朝大诗人杜甫（712~770）的颂称。", "block_bbox": [329, 1480, 1943, 1603], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 12}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "3.耽思乎经籍；图像于凌烟。", "block_bbox": [423, 1626, 991, 1674], "block_id": 12, "block_order": 13}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "上联典指晋朝时期的杜预，博学多通，耽思经籍，为《春秋左氏经传集解》，又作《盟会图》《春秋长历》，成一家之言。下联典指唐朝时期的杜如晦与房玄龄共管朝政，史称“房谋杜断”，后图其像于凌烟阁。", "block_bbox": [328, 1698, 1945, 1892], "block_id": 13, "block_order": 14}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "4.花折应时，金陵度曲；兰谪降丽，玉简留珍。", "block_bbox": [426, 1917, 1353, 1964], "block_id": 14, "block_order": 15}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "此联又简作：金陵度曲；玉简遗珍。", "block_bbox": [428, 1989, 1140, 2036], "block_id": 15, "block_order": 16}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "上联典指唐朝时期的金陵女子杜秋娘撰《金缕衣》诗。下联典指东汉道姑杜兰香（传为仙女），降于洞庭包山张硕家，留玉简唾孟等具，授张硕以道，硕成仙而去。\n", "block_bbox": [330, 2060, 1944, 2256], "block_id": 16, "block_order": 17}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "5.新年载酒寻花市，人日题诗寄草堂。", "block_bbox": [426, 2282, 1174, 2330], "block_id": 17, "block_order": 18}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "上联见杜甫诗。下联句见唐代诗人高适诗《人日寄杜二拾遗》。", "block_bbox": [428, 2355, 1664, 2408], "block_id": 18, "block_order": 19}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "6.卜筑草堂，误传严武宅；驰名武库，癖好左氏书。", "block_bbox": [425, 2431, 1449, 2480], "block_id": 19, "block_order": 20}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "上联典指四川省成都杜甫草堂。后人误以为是严武的故居。下联典指西晋将领、学者杜预事典。\n", "block_bbox": [328, 2504, 1942, 2625], "block_id": 20, "block_order": 21}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "7.南阳世泽；莱国家声。", "block_bbox": [425, 2651, 905, 2700], "block_id": 21, "block_order": 22}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9390220642089844, "coordinate": [330.9642333984375, 2060.938720703125, 1944.5577392578125, 2256.306884765625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9355849623680115, "coordinate": [327.50177001953125, 466.1035461425781, 1938.3837890625, 658.087646484375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9324145317077637, "coordinate": [328.74017333984375, 1698.86376953125, 1945.3017578125, 1892.8037109375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9233519434928894, "coordinate": [328.462158203125, 2504.2255859375, 1942.0595703125, 2625.1142578125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.907529354095459, "coordinate": [327.94293212890625, 254.52337646484375, 1938.654296875, 374.471923828125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9056768417358398, "coordinate": [329.2886962890625, 679.236328125, 1937.9898681640625, 802.462158203125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8939699530601501, "coordinate": [329.6497802734375, 1480.921142578125, 1943.0955810546875, 1603.521728515625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8846296668052673, "coordinate": [327.92413330078125, 1261.42236328125, 1941.909423828125, 1384.537109375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8581763505935669, "coordinate": [426.72955322265625, 2282.39013671875, 1174.3134765625, 2330.486328125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8553172945976257, "coordinate": [428.162841796875, 1989.6031494140625, 1140.380859375, 2036.7647705078125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8478774428367615, "coordinate": [428.6644287109375, 2355.9755859375, 1664.5924072265625, 2408.4169921875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8457528352737427, "coordinate": [421.0841064453125, 396.02288818359375, 1406.2987060546875, 445.10107421875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8411983251571655, "coordinate": [426.3210144042969, 1917.1982421875, 1353.259521484375, 1964.85107421875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8395129442214966, "coordinate": [425.27740478515625, 2431.9814453125, 1449.346435546875, 2480.0126953125]}, {"cls_id": 0